message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you the product for $14,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price.
I appreciate your time and consideration, but I was thinking more along the lines of $12,000. Would you be willing to meet me at that price?
Bob, I understand your position, but $12,000 is quite low for the value this product offers. Would you consider $13,000? It's a fair compromise.
I appreciate your willingness to compromise, but I'm still a bit short of my budget. Would you be willing to meet me at $12,500?
